msgid "Quarkus Base Runtime Image"
msgstr "Quarkus 基础运行时镜像"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To ease the containerization of native executables, Quarkus provides a base image providing the requirements to run these executables.\n"
"The `ubi9-quarkus-micro-image:2.0` image is:"
msgstr "为了简化原生可执行文件的容器化过程，Quarkus 提供了一个基础镜像，其中包含运行这些可执行文件所需的组件。 `ubi9-quarkus-micro-image:2.0` 镜像如下："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "small (based on `ubi9-micro`)"
msgstr "小型（基于 `ubi9-micro` ）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "designed for containers"
msgstr "专为集装箱设计"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "contains the right set of dependencies (glibc, libstdc++, zlib)"
msgstr "包含正确的依赖项（glibc、libstdc++、zlib）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "support upx-compressed executables (more details on the xref:upx.adoc[enabling compression documentation])"
msgstr "支持 UPX 压缩的可执行文件（更多详细信息请参阅 xref:upx.adoc[“启用压缩”文档] ）"

